@node Main "Balaby - Documentation"

                              'Balaby'  1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Balaby' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where you have to move a ball from
a starting position towards the 'Exit', indicated by an 'E', in the
least amount of moves. This is done by @{" rotating " link play} the game board,
either clockwise or counterclockwise, so the ball falls down,
following the law of physics; I.E.: From the upper part toward the
lower part of the game board.

  To complicate matters a little: only a 4 by 4 spaces portion of
the entire 8 by 8 size game board is visible at any time.

  As you complete a game board, Balaby displays a new board and the
game continues...

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
