@node features "Features"

                               Features

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-Many game boards to play with.

-Balaby is a 'Workbench' game, so it is meant to be played on the
 Workbench screen. The game window can be resized up to a maximum
 of 640 x 400 pixels, and the game is redisplayed according to the
 new window size. If the window is too small, it will automatically
 be resized to an adequate displayable size.

-As the game uses as little of the computer's ressources as
 possible, you can run other applications, games, etc. at the same
 time.

-Balaby works on all Amigas with Workbench 1.3 or higher.

@endnode

